    <string name="tutorial_page_find_title">Welcome to OddSpot!</string>
    <string name="tutorial_page_find_description">Your adventure begins here. Use the map to identify and navigate to intriguing spots nearby. Once you\'re at the location in real life, simply click on the marker in the app to unlock more details about the spot and earn points! You can also discover new and exciting locations by searching for spots based on their distance from you or by using tags. Prepare yourself to explore and uncover hidden gems around you!</string>
    <string name="tutorial_page_submit_title">Ready to share your own discoveries?</string>
    <string name="tutorial_page_submit_description">Capture a photo of the fascinating location or object, add an engaging title, and provide a concise description to help other users appreciate its uniqueness. You can also include additional details like tags to make your spot more discoverable. Once you\'re finished, hit submit, and after our validation process, your spot will be added to the map for everyone to enjoy!</string>
    <string name="tutorial_page_profile_title">Explore Your Profile &amp; Progress</string>
    <string name="tutorial_page_profile_description">There, you\'ll find your personal info, as well as the spots you\'ve created and visited. Remember to explore the settings section to personalize your app experience and update your account details.</string>
    <string name="tutorial_page_warning_title">Safety first!</string>
    <string name="tutorial_page_warning_description">When exploring new spots, always be mindful of your surroundings and follow local laws and regulations. Remember that some locations may be on private property or restricted areas, so always respect the boundaries and exercise caution. We encourage you to be responsible adventurers and leave the places you visit as you found them, so others can enjoy them too. Happy exploring!</string>
    <string name="tutorial_page_gdpr_title">Your privacy is important to us!</string>
    <string name="tutorial_page_gdpr_description">In accordance with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), we are committed to protecting your personal information and being transparent about how we collect, use, and store it. Rest assured that your data is used solely to enhance your app experience and is never shared with third parties without your explicit consent. For more information on our privacy practices, please refer to our Privacy Policy and Terms of Service.</string>

